// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2024-1542 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: 8cd58d83-c2d3-5f22-9afe-cd9b55942a6f

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*debian:10*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:11*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:12*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:9*")
